    person("Yuan", "Qi", email = "ayqi@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Implements copula-based sensitivity analysis and worst-case partial identification methods for estimating long-term treatment effects using surrogate outcomes. The package includes tools for nuisance estimation based on 'glmnet', 'grf', and 'xgboost'.
